## CastKIT.not property

Safely casts to exclude the type checked by the provided predicate.

**Signature:**

```typescript
not: <TIn, TExclude extends TIn>(predicate: TypePredicate<TIn, TExclude>, message?: string) => <TSource extends TIn>(value: TSource) => Exclude<TSource, TExclude>;
```
